data.meta_site_name: The Official Web Site of Derek Fisher . Analyst . Coach . Five-Time NBA World Champion
data.text:
Five-time NBA Champion Derek Fisher’s passion for impacting the lives of young people motivated him to create a camp experience for children and teens of all skill levels. DFBA is dedicated and focused on developing the basketball, leadership and life skills of each camper. Derek and his team are prepared now more than ever to elevate campers to the next level both on and off the court.

Learn more about the camp from Derek in the videos below.
